nodes.text: "Let's Go!" was a short story written by Peter M. Schweighofer and published in the Shadows of the Empire Sourcebook.
Rogue Squadron pilots Wedge Antilles and Wes Janson covertly orbit Coruscant in their X-wing fighters, waiting for Dash Rendar's signal moments before the Battle over Coruscant.
